<div id="outline-container-sec-3-0-2" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-3-0-2"><span class="section-number-4">3.0.2</span> Aug - Dec, 2008</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-3-0-2">
<p>
<b>Study of phase transitions in mechanical models</b>
</p>

<p>
The project involved the study, observation of the phases and
plotting the phase transitions in a simple mechanical model using
MATLAB as a tool. A simple model of a sphere rolling down the
surface of another sphere was considered and the phase transitions
between the pure rolling, rolling with slipping and detached
phases were studied.
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-sec-3-0-2-0-1" class="outline-6">
<h6 id="sec-3-0-2-0-1"><span class="section-number-6">3.0.2.0.1</span> Mentor</h6>
<div class="outline-text-6" id="text-3-0-2-0-1">
<p>
Dr. A.K. Biswas, Physics, BITS-Pilani, Goa Campus
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-3-0-3" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-3-0-3"><span class="section-number-4">3.0.3</span> Aug - Dec, 2007</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-3-0-3">
<p>
<b>Simulation of class room acoustics</b>
</p>

<p>
The project involved simulation of class-room acoustics using the
method of images, in general, and the Allen-Berkeley algorithm in
particular, to obtain the reverberation time profile of a cuboid
shaped classroom and to identify the `acoustically' best
locations. MATLAB was used to write and simulate the code.
</p>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-sec-3-0-3-0-1" class="outline-6">
<h6 id="sec-3-0-3-0-1"><span class="section-number-6">3.0.3.0.1</span> Mentor</h6>
